                    Wahu®, consultable en <a
                        href="https://wahustreaming.com/privacy-policy"
                        class="text-lime-400 underline"
                        >https://wahustreaming.com/privacy-policy</a
                    >.
                </p>

                <p class="text-xl font-bold">2. Servicio</p>
                <p>
